           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7933-5265")))
Description: Nonparametric local polynomial estimator for multivariate density
    functions on known domains of arbitrary dimension, including complicated
    domains with sharp concavities, holes, and local pinches such as polynomial
    sectors. Implements the procedure of Bertin, Klutchnikoff and Ouimet
    (Bernoulli, forthcoming).
